blog.name: good-omens-fanart
blog.title: Good Omens fan art collection
blog.description: A curated collection of fan art for the book Good Omens (by Terry Pratchett and Neil Gaiman) and its adaptations (including a radio play and a TV miniseries).

summary: GOOD OMENS FANART CHALLENGE (number one)
title: GOOD OMENS FANART CHALLENGE (number one)
body:
Creators of fanart!  Everyone and their mouse circus has made art of the demon and the angel, but these characters from the Dramatis Personae at the front of Good Omens have next to no art of them.  I challenge you to make some. 

  • Witchfinder Major Thou-Shalt-Not-Commit-Adultery Pulsifer 
  • Mr. Young 
  • Mr. R.P. Tyler 
  • The Delivery Man

Go make good art!  (And post it on tumblr with #good omens.)

Feeling rather ineffable these days. Expect a great deal of Good Omens.

Pratchett. Wodehouse.
Cats. The Doctors Whom. Science. Cute things. Life truths. Pixels. And spiders, sometimes, so keep that in mind.

My work with Vyc on a Kardasi conlang is here.
